# Guest Reservation Portal  
### Casa Tente Boutique Hotel

## Project Overview
The **Guest Reservation Portal** is a web-based reservation and management system developed for **Casa Tente Boutique Hotel**. The system was designed to replace the hotel’s manual reservation process by automating room booking, availability checking, email notifications, and administrative reporting. It aims to reduce overbooking issues, improve operational efficiency, and enhance customer satisfaction through real-time data management.

This project was developed as a **Capstone Project** in partial fulfillment of the requirements for the **Bachelor of Science in Information Systems**.

